## Name

gunzip

## Synopsis

```sh
$ gunzip [--keep] [--stdout] <FILE...>
```

## Options:

* `--help`: Display help message and exit
* `--version`: Print version
* `-k`, `--keep`: Keep (don't delete) input files
* `-c`, `--stdout`: Write to stdout, keep original files unchanged

## Arguments:

* `FILE`: File to decompress
